Get the executables (Pcrystal and Pproperties) from Box
[Lucas' weekly meeting/Useful files/crystal/crystal17_cc-login
https://uofi.app.box.com/folder/40966375791

How to compile
- Get crystal17_v1_0_1_Linux-ifort17_emt64_Pdistrib.tar.gz 
> tar -zxvf crystal17_v1_0_1_Linux-ifort17_emt64_Pdistrib.tar.gz
> module load openmpi/1.4-gcc+ifort
> module load intel/17.0
> cd build/Xmakes
- Set the variable MPIBIN in Linux-ifort17_XE_emt64.inc to be MPIBIN = /usr/local/openmpi-1.4-intel/bin
> cd ..
> make parallel
- The executable crystal, properties, Pcrystal and Pproperties will be written in bin/Linux-ifort17_XE_emt64/v1_0_1.
